    "description": "We at HUDCO Holdings Services are looking for an experienced Sales Manager based out of Nashik. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout HUDCO Holdings Services:\nHUDCO Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with HUDCO Holdings Services!",
